---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SiteHeader from '../components/SiteHeader.astro';
const lang = 'zh';
---

<BaseLayout
  title={`${lang === 'zh' ? '关于' : 'About'} | Hans Cao Photograph`}
  description="About Hans Cao and this photography archive."
>
  <SiteHeader lang={lang} />
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-14 lg:px-10">
    <section class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[280px_1fr] lg:items-start">
      <div class="flex justify-center lg:justify-start">
        <img
          src="/images/about-avatar.png"
          alt="Hans 头像"
          class="h-52 w-52 rounded-full object-cover object-center lg:h-56 lg:w-56"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-5 text-zinc-700" style="font-family: 'Kaiti SC', 'STKaiti', 'KaiTi', serif;">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">欢迎来到 Hans 的摄影网站！</h1>

        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed">🆔：法学生，摄影爱好者。</p>
        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed">📍：🇨🇳北京；🇲🇴澳门</p>
        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed">📸：记录光影、人文、风光、故事与日常瞬间等。</p>
        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed">📷：iPhone x Fujifilm x Canon</p>

        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed">这个网站是我的个人影像档案，用来持续记录和整理摄影作品。</p>

        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed">
          欢迎访问
          <a href="/works" class="font-semibold underline underline-offset-4">作品页</a>
          查看我的收藏。你也可以点击任意照片查看详情：地点、时间、器材等信息。
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
